                            notBefore="1988-10-05T01:43:00+00:00">undated</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>[Source: Reagan Library, <gloss target="#t_NSC_1">
                        <orgName corresp="recft7WGb7Fww0wma">NSC</orgName>
                    </gloss> Intelligence Files, 1988 SYS IV <gloss target="#t_RWR_1">RWR</gloss>
                    INT (1989 to end of <gloss target="#t_RWR_1">RWR</gloss>
                    <rs type="event" corresp="recrvfeHjk0YIZ1si">Administration</rs> 1/20/89
                    8940001-8940019. Top Secret; [handling restrictions not declassified]. Four
                    pages not declassified.]</p>
            </frus:attachment>
